    Megatron looks to Kitkat, "I suggest a treaty with the Allience. Our 
might would crush the Maximals, and stamp out all the other disgusting little 
groups that pain us. Then, after all is settled.....we simply end the 
agreement and go about on our own agenda. And if it happens to be the 
destruction of the Allience, so be it. After all....I dont think it would be 
any sooner than a few months until the Maximals are on the decline."
    He looked at her wrist. There, blinking silently, was her commlink. Why 
was it blinking? What was the little doggie up to? "Um, darling, pray tell 
what is that blinking light on your commlink signify?" He said, gazing closer.
